# Coinage Database Migrations

## Overview
This directory contains database migration scripts for the Coinage project.

## Migration Management
- Uses Flask-Migrate for database schema version control
- Tracks incremental changes to database schema
- Supports rollback and upgrade of database structure

## Quick Reference

### Common Commands
- `flask db migrate`: Create a new migration script
- `flask db upgrade`: Apply pending migrations
- `flask db downgrade`: Revert last migration

## Best Practices
- Always backup database before migrations
- Review migration scripts before applying
- Test migrations in a staging environment

## Troubleshooting
- If migration fails, check model definitions
- Ensure all dependencies are installed
- Verify database connection settings
